creator: MMC Investment Company Limited
descriptionHtml:
Description
REIMAGINE OWNERSHIP.

Guarantee the authenticity of your artwork purchase with a simple tap. Through ZHEN.’s proprietary verification technology powered by blockchain, you’ll always know when you have the real artwork in your hands.

Art collectibles that feature our identification NFC chips will be verifiable through the ZHEN. app: Just look for “Authenticated by ZHEN.” or “Powered by ZHEN.” on the box.

With our app, you’ll be able to verify your ZHEN.-authenticated art collectibles with state-of-the-art technology in your palm.

What’s more on ZHEN.:
- Browse curated news and roundups from our editorial team
- Learn more about your favorite artists and artworks, exclusively on ZHEN.

Stay tuned for even more exciting features to come.
We look forward to exploring the art world together with you.
